{"tid":2000534,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【賽後檢討】五一黃金周小勝，策略完善討論","createTime":"2020-05-04T02:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T06:10:00.000Z","uid":205733,"like":27,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cf73819bb3fc94fd0e9ac278f171dbae71ac7240","tid":2000534,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:33:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>五一黃金周總結：</ins></span></span></strong><br />\n- 黃店大發市，藍店拍烏蠅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 黑警策劃炸彈案失敗，被雲海踢爆<br />\n雖然小勝，希望大家繼續討論<br />\n黃色經濟圈成長方向<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其實因爲黃色經濟圈威力强大，一直受到相當强烈攻擊，例如：</span></strong></span><br />\n- 共媒不斷攻擊黃色經濟圈攬炒，聲稱政治凌駕經濟<br />\n- 企圖邊緣化黃店/黃色經濟圈，減少其威力<br />\n- TVB/ 百份報 等共媒開始反擊，聯同黑警用刑事恐嚇罪拘捕手足 企圖威嚇市民<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins>調整方向：</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>- 黃色經濟圈 改名為良心經濟圈</ins></span></strong><br />\n吸納 淺黃/所謂中立及淺藍市場<br />\n清楚分級，按良知程度 懲罰<br />\n簡單講，你可以支持政府<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><ins>底綫係公平徹查所有警察犯法行爲<br />\n就係良知既底綫</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n但呢個級別只係不懲罰，但不推薦；<br />\n然後越黃越懲罰，增加威力。<br />\n基本上你要吸納佢地，然後經濟上利誘佢地，先可以繼續壯大黃色經濟圈<br />\n底綫畫得太高，其實拒絕有潛力變黃既 淺藍/中立店<br />\n同時邊緣化自己<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">改名為<ins><span style=\"color: green;\">良心經濟圈</span></ins>，一來減少政治味道，降低共媒標簽效應<br />\n圈如其名，有良心就可以參加，唔存在攬炒同打擊香港經濟<br />\n攬炒既只係無良心既仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>關於加力打擊共媒 TVB/ 百份報</strong></span></span><br />\n- 舉著藍旗反藍旗，代替直接出文抵制<br />\n邊個響 TVB/百份 賣廣告，大家就係深藍絲<br />\n大大力宣傳，支持721 支持警察打甲由，叫藍絲支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家自然識做，佢地又吹你唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同藍絲鬥藍，甚至開戰，分化藍絲；<br />\n- 雙重打擊，抵制 TVB/ 百份之餘，大家似乎忘記支持競爭對手<br />\n大家係咪忘記咗 TVB/ 百份 既競爭對手<br />\n當廣告商去TVB 落廣告，發覺生意額大幅減少，固然有用<br />\n當廣告商去ViuTv 落廣告，生意額大幅增加，攻擊力係兩倍<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩大家每日任務，除咗抵制 TVB/ 百份之外<br />\n同樣要爆買蘋果/ViuTV 廣告商 e.g 三菱電機<br />\n倍大黃色經濟圈威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f0766be6296a407ba3ebc5a67f86a744e5f3a842","tid":2000534,"uid":151313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:34:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c38ac81d3f69814a6c7309fa503a9112f8220e1f","tid":2000534,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:36:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c5777b8bd6b124a235efe3182db4704f48a396f","tid":2000534,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:37:14.000Z","msg":"歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead632e4a5483da6a5e78744b17505fad057c86a","tid":2000534,"uid":143582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:38:05.000Z","msg":"良心經濟圈個名好唔掂，將黃藍模糊化<br />\n<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"2146ce569cc86c0f265fb4edf2d0b8fe016d04a3","tid":2000534,"uid":130225,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:42:42.000Z","msg":"良心經濟圈好似d廢老改d名"},{"pid":"31ed8d7ea5e6b679bae277cc4765167e115488cf","tid":2000534,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ead632e4a5483da6a5e78744b17505fad057c86a","tid":2000534,"uid":143582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:38:05.000Z","msg":"良心經濟圈個名好唔掂，將黃藍模糊化<br />\n